Ahumada (trans.), in <em>Mexican Philosophy in the 20<sup>th</sup>
Century: Essential Readings</em>, Carlos Alberto S&aacute;nchez and
Robert Eli Sanchez (eds.), Oxford: Oxford University Press:
141&ndash;155.</li>

<li>Zea, L., 1968. &ldquo;Philosophy and Thought in Latin
America,&rdquo; <em>Latin American Research Review</em>, 3(2):
3&ndash;16.</li>

<li>Zea, L., 1952 [2017]. &ldquo;Philosophy as Commitment,&rdquo; Amy
Oliver (trans.), in <em>Mexican Philosophy in the 20<sup>th</sup>
Century: Essential Readings</em>, Carlos Alberto S&aacute;nchez and
Robert Eli Sanchez (eds.), Oxford: Oxford University Press:
125&ndash;140.</li>
</ul>

